                                "stop": 19.899,
                                "byte_start": 76800,
                                "byte_stop": 156421,
                                "text": "The disposition of number 72-1589, Richardson against Ramirez and 73-507 Hamling against the United States, 73-557, Jenkins against Georgia will each be announced by Mr. Justice Rehnquist."
